Subtitle of Senate Bill 325
TO AMEND THE ARKANSAS JUVENILE CODE OF 1989; TO AMEND THE CHILD
MALTREATMENT ACT; TO AMEND THE LAW REGARDING REINSTATEMENT OF
PARENTAL RIGHTS; AND TO AMEND THE LAW REGARDING THE CHILD
MALTREATMENT CENTRAL REGISTRY.
